```plantuml
@startuml gabrielfarah_OpenHub
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "GitHub"

package "OpenHub System" {
  rectangle "crawler.py" as Crawler #lightblue
  rectangle "RabbitMQ" as RabbitMQ #lightcoral
  rectangle "worker/manager.py" as Manager #lightgreen
  database "MongoDB" as MongoDB #lightyellow

  package "Analysis Modules" {
    rectangle "Security" as Security #lightpink
    rectangle "Testability" as Testability #lightpink
    rectangle "Reusability" as Reusability #lightpink
    rectangle "Usability" as Usability #lightpink
  }
}

GitHub --> Crawler : Fetch Repos
Crawler --> RabbitMQ : Publish Tasks
RabbitMQ --> Manager : Consume Tasks
Manager --> GitHub : Download Code
Manager --> Security : Run Security Tests
Manager --> Testability : Run Testability Tests
Manager --> Reusability : Run Reusability Tests
Manager --> Usability : Run Usability Tests
Manager --> MongoDB : Update Results
Crawler --> MongoDB : Store Metadata

note right of Crawler
  - Uses github3.py
  - Manages crawling logic
end note

note right of Manager
  - Consumes messages
  - Executes analysis
end note

note right of RabbitMQ
  - Message broker for tasks
end note

note right of MongoDB
  - Stores analysis results
  - Holds repository metadata
end note

note right of Analysis Modules
  - Modular structure
  - Plugin-based tests
end note

@enduml
```